581"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：X（推特）</figcaption></figure><p> Meica 最初以 Hina Misora（隶属于 WACTOR Productions）作为 VTuber，是来自拉丁美洲最受欢迎的艺人之一。</p><p>美卡此次获得的10万订阅者数量，大约相当于日南空时期订阅者数量的一半。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="675" data-attachment-id="103590" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-meica-reaches-100k-youtube-subscribers/meica_youtube_channel_october_17_2023/" data-orig-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/meica_youtube_channel_october_17_2023.png" data-orig-size="1200,675" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="meica_youtube_channel_october_17_2023" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/meica_youtube_channel_october_17_2023.png" data-large-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/meica_youtube_channel_october_17_2023.png" src="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/meica_youtube_channel_october_17_2023.png" alt="" class="wp-image-103590"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"> Meica Ch.（截至 2023 年 10 月 17 日） </figcaption></figure><p></p><div class="ozdrh652f5bf0a244e" ><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3186024119059876"
