</style><p>布斯波！自2月1日小森Meto加入公司以来，公司持续录得显着增长，人均注册用户数高位增长，到4月28日，人均注册会员数有所增长。就订户数量而言，该频道已升至日本第二位。到 2023 年，我们将成为发展最快的办事处和集团之一。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="Bm4mlmygRB"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-group-vspo-announces-overseas-expansion/">VTuber团体Buspo！海外扩张公告，英文区和中文区启动全球海选</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“VTuber Group Buspo！宣布海外扩张，在英语和中国国家开始全球选拔” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-group-vspo-announces-overseas-expansion/embed/#?secret=xgWDRl5Pni#?secret=Bm4mlmygRB" data-secret="Bm4mlmygRB" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="m07L1PnMFf"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-group-vspo-recorded-the-largest-increase-in-youtube-subscribers-as-of-june-25-2023-for-all-agencies-and-groups/">VTuber团体Buspo！截至6月25日，订阅人数增幅是所有机构和团体中最高的。</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“VTuber Group Buspop！截至6月25日频道订阅人数增幅是所有经纪公司和团体中最高的” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-group-vspo-recorded-the-largest-increase-in-youtube-subscribers-as-of-june-25-2023-for-all-agencies-and-groups/embed/#?secret=gSt4HeUrKP#?secret=m07L1PnMFf" data-secret="m07L1PnMFf" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="5Ii0dqzzbl"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-youtube-subscribers-information-agencies-and-groups-o